Heston Blumenthal's Fat Duck Restaurant in Bray, Berkshire was named the eighth best restaurant in the world in the annual poll by luxury travel magazine Elite Traveler . 
  Dinner by Heston Blumenthal also made it into the top 25 of the list . 
  Alinea in Chicago was crowned the world's best restaurant for the fourth year in a row . 
  Raymond Blanc's Le Manoir Aux Quat' Saisons was also in the top 100 . 
 